               <p>I am a <rs id="t17830430-53-viclabel295" type="occupation">cabinet-maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830430-53-victim691 t17830430-53-viclabel295"></join>, I lost two waistcoats from my back room, on the first floor, at the house of 
               <persName id="t17830430-53-person693">
                  Thomas
                   Taylor
               <interp inst="t17830430-53-person693" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830430-53-person693" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830430-53-person693" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
