                     <interp inst="t17830430-53-person695" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I went for the waistcoats, the pawnbroker has got the duplicate, and has sent his note in writing.</p>
               <p>(The note read.)</p>
               <p>"These are the waistcoats pledged with me by 
               <persName id="t17830430-53-person696">
                  William
                   Rardy
               <interp inst="t17830430-53-person696" type="surname" value="Rardy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830430-53-person696" type="given" value="William"></interp>
